WEBVTT

00:05:59.328 --> 00:06:02.500
We need a participation revolution,

00:06:02.500 --> 00:06:05.374
and we need it fast.

00:06:05.374 --> 00:06:10.712
The idea of voting as our 
only exercise in citizenship

00:06:10.712 --> 00:06:13.670
does not make sense anymore.

00:06:13.670 --> 00:06:16.199
People are tired of only being treated

00:06:16.199 --> 00:06:20.372
as empowered individuals every few years

00:06:20.372 --> 00:06:23.522
when it's time to delegate that power

00:06:23.522 --> 00:06:25.897
to someone else.

00:06:25.897 --> 00:06:28.842
If the protests that swept Brazil

00:06:28.842 --> 00:06:33.814
in June 2013 have taught us anything,